::Zardus/Mosquitor::

Zardus nods. "Yes. We'll redesign them a bit first though. Relations 
with the Predacons are going allright. There's no point in letting it 
be clear that we've captured three of their troops."

He turns back to the shuttles. "Allright. Hurricane, Wheeljack, you 
and the two femms you have will ride in the second shuttle. 
Mosquitor, this one, and I will ride in the other one. We're heading 
back to base and then to Lab 2 to get convert these femms into 
Alliance members."

Mosquitor's head jerks up. "Alliance?" the bug protests, "These are 
Predacon property, for Hell Beast!"

With an annoyed growl Zardus looks back at Mosquitor. "Yes, that's 
what I meant, Mosquitor, we'll program them to Predacon." He sighs. 
Mosquitor would have to be taken care of as well. "Allright, lets get 
going. We'll meet up back at base."

He enters the shuttle with Aelo, Mosquitor entering behind him. His 
shuttle would take off as soon as Hurricane and Wheeljack got into 
theirs.
